Jose Gonzalez has announced Vestiges & Claws, his first new solo album since 2007's In Our Nature. It's out February 17, 2015 via Mute, and was self-produced by Gonzalez in Gothenburg, Sweden. Since the release of In Our Nature, Gonzalez recorded two studio albums with Junip and contributed to the soundtrack for The Secret Life of Walter Mitty.
